AMCC Change Log
v1.5.4

Thanks to qiuzilu for providing a Chinese translation 
and making me aware of an issue with Unicode characters!

Caution! This release is yet to be tested! Please report any Issues!

[+] Added:
- Partial Chinese translation.
- Chinese (and other Unicode) characters support for chat
- New option in preferences under "General" tab for changing display mode of Unicode characters:
  - Autmatic (Default) - Font will be adjusted on the fly to display Unicode characters
  - Force Custom Font - Old behavior, Unicode font will almost never be used (Except for GUI elements in Chinese language)
  - Force Unicode Font - Completely unload Minecraftia font, and use only Unicode font